# Project Intelligence & Context

This project uses `graphify` for architectural context and documentation.

## Context Retrieval
- Before answering architectural or codebase questions, read `graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md` for god nodes and community structure.
- If `graphify-out/wiki/index.md` exists, prioritize it for navigation.

## Maintenance
- After modifying code files in a session, run `graphify update .` to keep the graph current (AST-only, no API cost).
- If the project structure changes significantly, run `graphify cluster-only .` to update community groupings.

## Project Files
- Always consult `AGENTS.md` for core principles and `TASK.md` for current progress.
- Respect the "Live Test" rule: don't mark tasks as done without operational verification.
